name: Men's 'Marshal' Jacket (Serpentis)
description: This jacket indicates, with a casual but deadly certainty, that the wearer is a proud supporter of the Serpentis. Its slanted lines in shiny gold over the shoulder and forearms give the impression of a potential for unimaginable speed. Meanwhile, the darker outlines running up front and back - in a column rising through the spine and chest and eventually fountaining up through the shoulders - remind any onlookers that they're looking at a man of immense power.
